# Private data + heavy model objects live OUTSIDE git, in an Insync-synced
# "srw_behaviour-store" folder, symlinked into the repo by setup.sh (request the
# data from the authors — see README). Ignored by bare name so the symlinks
# themselves are never committed (a trailing-slash pattern would not match one).
